MonitorGizmo
------------
- attributes
  * type: CRT, LCD, etc
  * size: 15, 17, 19, 21, etc
- behaviors
  * initialize(type, size)
  * update_tally(count)
    calls super(bucket, count)
    . add(count)
    . subtract(count)
  * update_amount
